messages.text: Anna, you there?
Yeah, I’m with Eve back at my apartment.
So Emily contacted me
What!?
Yeah, she was on the airplane.
First that trenchant bitch Dr. Smith was maneuvering some sort of
lazy puppetry with her telling me that...
they were going to be taken to a resort for safety...
but after one of the clones knocked her out, she told me the truth
Which was what
They are being taken to a place called Saint X in the Ukraine, or so she thinks.
THE UKRAINE
Yeah. So the good news is, I have a guy in the Ukraine. Anton
What does that mean, you have a guy in the Ukraine?
I have a guy. He does things. He is also a guy who has guys.
And I think they’ll be able to get them out of there.
I said that we would meet them in the next 48 hours
You already talked to this guy?
I’m talking to him while I’m talking to you.
Modern tech FTW
So what the hell is he saying
He’s having one of his guys check it out.
And how do we know he’s a reliable person and not
just going to sell the girls into being sex slaves
Did we meet under seedy circumstances?
Yes.
But unlike you, he knows how to execute these types of things.
He’s not sloppy about just setting off bombs like
they’re drunken text messages to ex-boyfriends at 2am.
He’s also not a pimp. And he owes me a few favors.
I don’t even want to know why.
Yeah, it’s better that you don’t ask.
Just know that he’ll get the job done. We need to be there.
How are we getting over there though?
You and Eve have a passport?
Yeah. Well, I do, but Eve doesn’t.
Though I don’t really have the money to fly to the Ukraine.
Yeah, that’s my problem too. However -
when I was looking into Eve’s background...
it looks like her parents are loaded
You’re suggesting that Eve steal from her parents!?
The fuckers have been in on it...
why not have them fund our recon mission?
Ask her.
She doesn’t have a passport, but...
she said she’d get the money.
Great!
Also, Anton is saying that his guy will probably need money to execute this.
I thought you said he owes you favors??
He does. His guys don’t.
Eve wants to know how much…
$10 grand
She almost fainted.
How the hell is she supposed to take all of this without her parents noticing…
Well, you know, I have my friend The Monkey.
If we can get access into her parents' account...
he can maneuver getting out the funds.
What info do you need?
What’s Eve's dad's full name?
Martin Thomas Childs.
Social security number?
Wait, if you get that...
what are you going to drain his bank account?
Something like that
But if you do that, won’t the bank shut down his account??
For strange activity buying plane tickets etc?
Dear, amateur Anna, we’re going to take out one large chunk of cash...
so just trust the criminals okay?
Fine. His social security number 503-05-0756
Egg salad.
What?
My way of saying excellent
So what’s the plan then?
Once we have the money, and we forward it to Anton’s guy.
We’ll be able to go more ahead with the plan.
But for now, we need to get the money
So what, do they do all the work?
They’ll probably bring them to us
Will they give us weapons?
We can probably have our pick, but not sure how involved we’ll be.
Again, more details along with the money.
How long will it take you to get the money?
The Monkey is a genius.
He’ll probably have it done in…
Oh wait, he has it done!
So what now?
Now, you need to pack your bags and meet me
at the Burger King on Wiley Pike.
The Burger King!?
Yes, I like to drink chocolate milkshakes before...
possibly being shot to death during international incidents.
See you there.
Click below to see what happens next...
